    					<div class="col-md-4 col-xs-4">
    						<h1 id="header-logo" class="image-text">
    							<a href="$!{env.appUrl}/index.htm">
    								<span class="mask"></span>
    								<span class="behind"></span>
    								<i class=""></i>
    							</a>
    						</h1>
    					</div>
    					<div class="col-md-8 col-xs-8">
    						<nav id="top-nav">
    							<ul class="nav-list transistion">
									<li><a class="active" href="$!{env.appUrl}/index.htm">关于</a></li>
    								<li><a href="$!{env.appUrl}/work/index.htm">工作</a></li>
    								<li><a href="$!{env.appUrl}/notes/index.htm">联系我们</a></li>
    							</ul>
    						</nav>
    					</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</header>
			
			<div class="masthead-wrap">
				<div id="title">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="transistion cloud left-cloud"></div>
						<div class="transistion cloud right-cloud"></div>
    					<div class="row">
    						<div class="col-md-12">
    							<div id="head-slider" class="transistion">
    								<div class="slide-contents">
    									<div class="slide">
    										<h2 class="im-sean">
    											<figure class="transistion">
    												<img src="$!{env.imgUrl}/image/portal/im-sean.svg" />
    											</figure>
    										</h2>
    										<p class="header-desc">a web designer.</p>
    									</div>
    								</div>
    							</div>
    						</div>
    					</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
	
			<div class="masthead-wrap">
    			<div id="masthead">
    				<div id="earth-holder">
    					<img src="$!{env.imgUrl}/image/portal/land.svg" />
    				</div>
    			</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="hello">
    		<div class="container">
    			<div class="row">
    				<div class="col-md-12">
    					<article>
    						<figure>
    							<img src="$!{env.imgUrl}/image/portal/me.svg" />
    						</figure>
    						<h3>Hi.</h3>
    						<p>
								杭州哇咖网络科技有限公司，致力于为高价值品牌提供信息化一站式服务，包括微信服务号建设，代运营；营销方案策划；淘宝、天猫、京东等多渠道电商平台代运营、营销方案策划；企业门户网站设计；企业信息化服务。
							</p>
    					</article>
    				</div>
    			</div>
    		</div>
		</section>

		#parse("/portal/framework/breaker.vm")
	
    	<section id="what-i-do">
    		<div class="container">
    			<div class="row">
    				<div class="col-md-12">
    					<article>
							<header>
    							<h2>我们...</h2>
    						</header>
    						<div id="design" class="row">
    							<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1">
									<div class="home-design-info">
										<figure>
    										<img src="$!{env.imgUrl}/image/portal/me.svg" />
    									</figure>
    									<div class="bubble right">
    										<div class="bubbling-design-icons-vert"></div>
   										</div>
									</div>
    							</div>
    							<div class="col-md-6">
    								<div class="deets">
    									<h3>团队</h3>
    									<p>
											团队成员在软件开发、运营、设计、客服、仓储物流、企业管理等领域有实战经验，尤其是在快速消费品行业具有资深服务经验，拥有严谨务实的实操标准体系。团队成员100%本科以上学历，具备创新、学习和不断追求卓越的要求和能力！
										</p>
    								</div>
    							</div>
    						</div>
    						<div id="develop" class="row">
    							<div class="col-md-4 col-md-push-7">
    								<div class="home-dev-info">
    									<figure>
    										<img src="$!{env.imgUrl}/image/portal/me-dev.svg" />
    									</figure>
										<div class="bubble left">
											<div class="bubbling-dev-icons-vert"></div>
										</div>			
    								</div>
    							</div>
    							<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-3">
									<div class="deets">
    									<h3>理想</h3>
    									<p>
											公司目前正处于高速发展之中，一群“爱学习！爱新鲜！爱炫！还有那么一点理想和情怀！”的年轻人聚在一起，做一点有意思的事！
										</p>
    								</div>
    							</div>
    						</div>
    					</article>
    				</div>
    			</div>
			</div>
    	</section>
	
		#parse("/portal/framework/footer.vm")
	
		#JSM(["jquery", "bootstrap"])
		<script type="text/javascript" src="$!{env.imgUrl}/js/portal/app.js"></script>
